{
  "stem": "21812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had my blonde hair, my blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so I raised my hand, I said, 'Heil Hitler,' and I passed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was scared-- scared as hell, because if he had stopped me, I mean, that would've been a very unpleasant, to say the least, experience.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I did go up and I delivered it and I came back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- but that was one of the last times that he actually sold anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people who, like in our building or some of the Gentiles we knew, they-- they sort of [INAUDIBLE] they removed themselves.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was never dis-- basically not discussed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was sort of a-- a retreat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They sort of retreated into their own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them, you know, were socialists before and really didn't believe in-- in what was going on, but just kept their mouth shut and didn't-- were afraid to support or give us any kind-- any kind of support.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was more of a, you know, hidden agenda.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were agencies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, eventually we-- when things became very, very bad, and towards the end of-- as l said, you know, my father lost his business or couldn't continue his business anymore.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we wanted to save every penny we had because we knew we would be leaving the country one way or another.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then eventually, we registered for a soup kitchen, which was part of the Jewish community, which had organized it and where you got food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that we did for a little while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then what my father did-- he was a very, very handy man, and he also loved to build things.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
